	* Programmer

		* pldoc_comment(?Object, ?Pos, -Summary, -Comment).

	  Comment is original string

	* Can be combined with XREF info and/or normal meta-info
	
	* Gathering can also be hooked into XREF by loading pldoc
	  and xref. [OK]

